name: Men's Red Parrot Print Tropical Shirt
description: A vibrant, vacation-ready shirt in a bold red. Features a classic all-over tropical print with purple parrots and green palm leaves, complete with a camp collar and chest pocket.

name: Men's Black Tropical Parrot Print Shirt
description: Make a statement with this classic black button-down. It features a lively all-over tropical print of colorful parrots, cockatoos, and lush palm leaves, finished with a relaxed camp collar.

name: Men's Red & White Hibiscus Print Shirt
description: A classic vacation-style shirt featuring a high-contrast, two-tone design. This bold red button-down is covered in a white hibiscus flower and palm leaf print, perfect for a standout tropical look.

name: Men's Brown & Black Vertical Stripe Shirt
description: A smart-casual button-down featuring a clean vertical stripe pattern in brown, black, and white. Designed with a classic collar and short sleeves for a sharp, modern look.

name: Men's Red Hot Rod Graphic Shirt
description: A high-octane button-down shirt featuring a vibrant, all-over graphic print. Includes a classic red muscle car with flames, a checkerboard pattern, and mechanic-style wrench graphics on a red brick background.

name: Men's "Extreme" Graffiti Print Shirt
description: Short Description: A modern casual shirt with a dynamic, all-over abstract print. This white button-down features graffiti-style "Extreme" text and geometric shapes in black, grey, and tan for a bold, streetwear-inspired look.

name: Men's Navy & Red Stripe Silky Shirt
description: A premium button-down shirt with a smooth, silky finish. Features a bold vertical stripe pattern in red and green against a dark navy background, complete with a relaxed camp collar and chest pocket.

name: Men's Retro Colorblock Panel Shirt
description: A vintage-style button-down shirt featuring a bold colorblock design. This black shirt has a classic camp collar and a striking central panel in blue and white.
